701817f-b.title: Bronx: Soundview Avenue - Rosedale Avenue
701817f-b.text:
(1)
Soundview Avenue, east side, at Rosedale Avenue (vantage point),
showing improvised shacks and coops. The view is northward.
May 1O, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
Another view across the site in an easterly direction.
May 1O, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
(3)
Another group of shacks in the same area.
May 1O, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
